legend right
  | <b>Protocol</b> | <b>Usage</b> |
  | HTTPS/REST | Frontend ↔ Backend |
  | SQLAlchemy/AsyncPG | Backend ↔ Database |
  | Telegram Bot API | Backend ↔ Telegram |
  | Multipart Form-Data | Image Uploads |
  | File I/O | File Storage Operations |
  | Dependency Injection | Router → Service |
  | ORM Queries | Service → Repository |
end legend

@enduml